Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.85,0:00:10.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cancelled!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.27,0:00:12.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The live breakup performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.65,0:00:13.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.98,0:00:17.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your group probably won't be able to fill\Nall of the seats in that hall anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.57,0:00:19.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's for your sake as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.95,0:00:22.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. President—hold on, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.86,0:00:26.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've worked so hard to arrange this live breakup performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.08,0:00:28.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is merely business as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.75,0:00:31.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't keep this up until we land ourselves in debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.79,0:00:34.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's it, how will we announce the split to the fans?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.09,0:00:37.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just write it on your homepage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.50,0:00:39.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or, if you'd like, I can do it for you, as I have before...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.97,0:00:44.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, I'll keep you employed for another six months...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.64,0:00:50.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it seems that you still have value as far as\Nvariety programs and talk shows are concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.89,0:00:52.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must be joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.69,0:00:55.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't you release me now since we can't\Ndo the live breakup performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.73,0:00:57.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:04.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Provided that you pay damages for breaking your\Ncontract and retiring earlier than planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.95,0:01:07.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.62,0:01:56.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The glorious future is just one step away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.50,0:01:58.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naturally, all my preparations are A-OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.45,0:02:00.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today's stage is a television station.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.02,0:02:02.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A brilliant masked world and a dangerous true face!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.30,0:02:04.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.78,0:02:06.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.51,0:02:08.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.16,0:04:00.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Filming at the television station's been suspended?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.75,0:04:01.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.50,0:04:03.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.79,0:04:05.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we were looking forward to it, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.96,0:04:09.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, the new Joker villain...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.84,0:04:12.03,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I thought we'd be able to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.84,0:04:12.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone's schedule got packed...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:16.35,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Something came up suddenly this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:16.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I thought I'd be able to eat the film shoot's lunch too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.64,0:04:19.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I invited you guys because the director\Nwas an acquaintance of mine, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.27,0:04:22.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems like they aren't able to show visitors around...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.98,0:04:24.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.44,0:04:26.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:30.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.32,0:04:33.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.24,0:04:39.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since we were already invited to the television\Nstation, we can just tour around while we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.16,0:04:40.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:42.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.54,0:04:44.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There should be a lot of famous people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.96,0:04:48.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi wants to meet the weather lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.17,0:04:49.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Toraya for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.80,0:04:50.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going for Yakkun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:59.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All while the famous idol Okino Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is right in front of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:00.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.39,0:05:03.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.46,0:05:06.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, it's Inoue Waka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.96,0:05:08.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.19,0:05:09.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The lady from Gochi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.32,0:05:13.46,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, good luck to you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:13.65,Signs,,0,0,0,,Inoue Waka
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:13.65,Signs,,0,0,0,,Actual Japanese Actress
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.03,0:05:14.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:16.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go easy on me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.53,0:05:19.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't her parents run a soba restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:20.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she has grilled eel...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:22.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:24.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inoue Waka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.48,0:05:26.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Birthdate: May 13th.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:29.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Height: 166 centimeters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.71,0:05:30.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.13,0:05:32.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.05,0:05:35.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:36.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.36,0:05:38.75,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:39.68,Signs,,0,0,0,,Yamamato Azusa
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:39.68,Signs,,0,0,0,,Actual Japanese Actress
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.81,0:05:45.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This time it's Yamamoto Azusa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:47.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Famous people all around...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.73,0:05:49.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.15,0:05:52.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okino Yoko, Inoue Waka, Yamamoto Azusa—wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.99,0:05:54.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.71,0:06:11.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But isn't that great?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.50,0:06:12.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were able to meet them all already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:13.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:17.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.97,0:06:19.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haven't we met before?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.97,0:06:22.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Azu also feels like she's met them before...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.02,0:06:28.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must have seen us in the newspaper or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:30.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because we are...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:32.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.36,0:06:34.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Detective Boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.78,0:06:39.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we're the Detective Boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:41.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We capture criminals and other bad guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.87,0:06:42.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.62,0:06:44.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.75,0:06:45.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:48.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.58,0:06:50.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Especially...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.75,0:06:55.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} here is a great detective on par with Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:07:00.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By "Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}," you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.76,0:07:02.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, Mouri Kogorou.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.14,0:07:05.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who's always supporting my efforts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.93,0:07:09.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, he is quite famous for being your fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:14.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess that means Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} will snatch away all the\Nquestions dealing with cases and deductions, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.82,0:07:16.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.82,0:07:18.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's this about questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:23.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're recording a quiz show today...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.95,0:07:26.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The three of us will be competing as contestants!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:31.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's why you said, "Good luck to you today."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:34.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, today our friendship is on-hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:36.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm turning my heart to stone so that I'll win for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:40.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.05,0:07:40.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.26,0:07:42.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is she a demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.47,0:07:43.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She sure is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.43,0:07:47.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.06,0:07:48.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi-cha—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:51.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:53.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It came!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:07:59.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.49,0:08:02.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the new K-K-Kamen Yaiba villain, aren't you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:10.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-Not just a villain—he must be the leader\Nof some sort of evil organization!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:12.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the new boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:13.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's got to be the boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.04,0:08:17.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this, brats?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.63,0:08:23.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You saying you really don't know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.85,0:08:25.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.10,0:08:31.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How disappointing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.19,0:08:39.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although I may not be that different from a Kamen Yaiba villain...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.99,0:08:43.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.45,0:08:46.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:48.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've never seen him before...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.66,0:08:49.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.66,0:08:54.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the vocalist from the rock group, "The Styx Three"...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.74,0:08:56.25,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Satan Onizuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.92,0:08:59.80,Signs,,0,0,0,,Satan Onizuka (32)\NVocalist for The Styx Three
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:03.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think I heard that he was supposed\Nto appear in a variety show today...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.72,0:09:08.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A rock singer in a variety show, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.18,0:09:11.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A devil's life sure is tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.27,0:09:15.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onizuka... Satan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:16.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.81,0:09:18.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onizuka Satan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:20.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satan Onizuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:22.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Mitsuhiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.61,0:09:23.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.53,0:09:26.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satan Onizuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:29.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel like I've heard that name somewhere before...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.04,0:09:36.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.58,0:09:40.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My sister asked me, because she's his... Satan Onizuka's fan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.63,0:09:44.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She asked me to get his autograph if I saw him at the television station!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.05,0:09:47.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I don't go after him and get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:51.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it looks like he's already gone off somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:55.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you taking this a bit too far?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.73,0:09:58.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.31,0:10:02.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We could at least find out where his\Ndressing room is if we ask Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.44,0:10:03.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.11,0:10:06.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:11.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So excited, so, so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.37,0:10:14.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} just here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.25,0:10:20.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The assistant director took her away just now, saying, "You're up."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:22.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Along with the other two contestants.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.17,0:10:28.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure it'll be all right if we search for him on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:29.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:33.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We at least know that he's somewhere in this television station.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.27,0:10:34.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.56,0:10:36.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we all search, we should be able to find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:40.20,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H383838&\3c&HFFFFFF&\b0}Satan Onizuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.65,0:10:46.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.49,0:10:50.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're already here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.12,0:10:55.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly, you didn't have\Nto show up until this afternoon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:57.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:10:59.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had nothing else to do, so I came early.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.17,0:11:03.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Manager, could you order\Nme some food to be delivered?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.55,0:11:06.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't had lunch yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.59,0:11:08.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.05,0:11:10.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.60,0:11:15.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ramen from Tenpuku-tei, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.31,0:11:18.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ramen from Tenpuku-tei...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.98,0:11:20.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fried rice from Jan Jan Ken.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.48,0:11:24.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fried rice from Jan Jan Ken, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.32,0:11:25.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:28.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some gyoza from Eirinan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:30.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gyoza from Eirinan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.07,0:11:35.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ramen, fried rice, and gyoza, all from different shops?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:38.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since those dishes are all Chinese, it'd be\Nbetter to order from the same shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.62,0:11:40.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.29,0:11:42.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I like those dishes from those particular shops.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.71,0:11:48.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, I eat at those three shops a lot, so even\Nif it's just one dish, I'd like to give them my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.05,0:11:51.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, reminds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.68,0:11:54.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you find the mirror I asked about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.10,0:11:56.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:12:00.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An acquaintance had seen something similar,\Nso I was actually on my way to that store now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.23,0:12:02.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:04.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.44,0:12:08.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without it, there's no way I'd be able to fix my makeup quite right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.65,0:12:09.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll get right on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.61,0:12:12.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.20,0:12:13.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, also...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.20,0:12:18.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to nap after I finish eating, so please\Ndon't wake me until it's time for my appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.29,0:12:20.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.62,0:12:25.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had an argument with the company president last\Nnight, and it bothered me so much I couldn't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:29.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly, he's here too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:33.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think he's in the meeting room two floors above this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.05,0:12:35.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.97,0:12:39.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess I have to go apologize to him after we finish filming...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.68,0:12:40.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:52.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, this television station sure is complicated...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:56.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One can't quite tell where anything is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.20,0:12:58.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even the toilets are hard to find, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.66,0:12:59.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's like a maze!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.37,0:13:03.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like it'd be better to ask someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.29,0:13:05.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, seems like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.22,0:13:19.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:29.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Early, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.73,0:13:31.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The meeting was supposed to be at 2:00...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.74,0:13:34.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.53,0:13:35.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry about last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.46,0:13:47.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A meeting at the television station, huh, Mr. President?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:52.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they wanted to use some talent from our\Ncompany as a regular for a new program...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.80,0:13:57.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you have a program to record at 2:00 as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.72,0:14:00.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you ready for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.43,0:14:01.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.60,0:14:04.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For that kind of thing, 30 minutes is more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.60,0:14:10.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, about that matter—it was I who turned them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:15.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You might be angry, but it was for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:18.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right; let's not talk about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.37,0:14:22.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take a look at this—what do you think of my raincoat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.62,0:14:27.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's light and water-repelling...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:28.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On top of that, it was cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.71,0:14:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's good...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.55,0:14:35.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want to know what part I like about it most?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.22,0:14:38.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I put the hood on like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.48,0:14:54.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's harder for the blood splatter to get on my person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.44,0:14:56.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pretty handy, I'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.47,0:15:13.47,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H383838&\3c&HFFFFFF&\b0}Satan Onizuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.71,0:15:14.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:16.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satan Onizuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.80,0:15:18.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt that this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.72,0:15:20.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.43,0:15:23.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but do you think this is polite?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:24.89,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H383838&\3c&HFFFFFF&\b0}\h\h\h\h\hSatan Onizuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:24.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seeing him without an appointment...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.77,0:15:28.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He might get mad at us with that scary face...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.48,0:15:30.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.19,0:15:33.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of people passing through this hallway...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.32,0:15:35.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it turns bad, we can call for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.19,0:15:38.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this "call for help"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.99,0:15:41.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna knock, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:44.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:47.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:49.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s in the middle of a nap right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.46,0:15:52.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He sleeps?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.75,0:15:54.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.21,0:15:57.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.26,0:16:02.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I don't, my powers won't recharge!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.39,0:16:07.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.56,0:16:09.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you please sign this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:13.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My sister's a big fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.53,0:16:25.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Name?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.33,0:16:28.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:31.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The "Asa" character from "breakfast," and "beautiful"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.46,0:16:33.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"For my true believer Asami."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.38,0:16:38.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.59,0:16:42.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.01,0:16:46.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With this, your sister becomes a member of our demon clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.06,0:16:51.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's origami!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:16:57.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.98,0:17:01.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So many cranes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.74,0:17:03.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.20,0:17:10.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you fold all of these?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.62,0:17:11.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.79,0:17:16.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While lying in wait, I occasionally partake in human pastimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.88,0:17:20.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I wasn't able to fold more than those five today...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.26,0:17:24.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this ruler doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.13,0:17:27.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Using the ruler, I can better fold them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.31,0:17:33.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, a devil folding origami—doesn't it ruin your image?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.98,0:17:35.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.19,0:17:39.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I forbid you to tell even my true believers...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.69,0:17:43.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's revealed, I'll put a death curse on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.78,0:17:48.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.95,0:17:50.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, Satan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.66,0:17:52.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have the mirror you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.12,0:17:54.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.54,0:17:55.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was this one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.79,0:17:56.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.46,0:17:57.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.42,0:18:01.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With this, I can do my makeup even in the dressing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.63,0:18:02.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.01,0:18:04.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:08.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.22,0:18:12.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, my contact just shifted a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.73,0:18:15.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:16.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:19.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Mitsuhiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:21.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You look pretty tense...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.94,0:18:24.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.57,0:18:28.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.28,0:18:30.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I also bought eye drops.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:32.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.79,0:18:35.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, set it over there for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.29,0:18:36.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.51,0:18:51.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, all the names on these plates and bowls are of different shops...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.43,0:18:52.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.39,0:18:56.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} has all kinds of strange tastes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.48,0:19:03.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's because human food really isn't up to my standards...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.57,0:19:11.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Patrol cars?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.74,0:19:13.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And an ambulance too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.54,0:19:18.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if something happened near here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.84,0:19:28.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It appears that "something" occurred at this TV station.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.09,0:19:31.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At this TV station?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.39,0:19:38.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.98,0:19:39.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.15,0:19:45.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, we're about to head to the studio...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:46.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.69,0:19:50.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The company president, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.86,0:19:51.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.70,0:19:54.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.12,0:19:55.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please come quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.95,0:19:56.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.83,0:19:57.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please clear the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.70,0:19:58.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.83,0:20:00.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satan Onizuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.08,0:20:00.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:02.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satan Onizuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:08.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.34,0:20:09.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:12.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.97,0:20:18.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. President!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.77,0:20:20.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. President!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.53,0:20:28.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who... in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.15,0:20:30.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.30,0:20:54.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The deceased is Urushibara Tenji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, president of an\Nentertainment production company, 47 years of age.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:57.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The estimated time of death is around 1:00 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.81,0:21:00.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cause of death is loss of blood via a bladed object.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.10,0:21:04.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the first person to discover the body was?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.94,0:21:06.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.27,0:21:15.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was supposed to be a meeting held here at 2:00 between Mr.\NUrushibara and the producer of the program I'm in charge of, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.24,0:21:19.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I came to tell him that we were going\Nto be a little late for the meeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.66,0:21:25.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I immediately called the police and ambulance, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.08,0:21:29.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the way, I notified Satan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} as well, who\Nalso belongs to the president's company...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.05,0:21:31.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.55,0:21:33.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.47,0:21:36.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.26,0:21:37.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A Death God!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.64,0:21:39.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am that Satan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.77,0:21:43.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satan Onizuka, the vocalist from The Styx Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.44,0:21:45.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,River Styx?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.15,0:21:46.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Santa Onizuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.52,0:21:48.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.61,0:21:50.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know of Satan Onizuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.86,0:21:53.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's from a visual kei rock band that\Nwas popular three or four years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:56.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey... Was popular?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.45,0:21:57.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're using past tense...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.95,0:22:01.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Regardless, do you know of anyone that\Nwould have a grudge against the president?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.29,0:22:06.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With his personality, I'm sure there were\Na lot of people with grudges against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.67,0:22:08.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Myself included.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.67,0:22:11.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, just to be sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.30,0:22:16.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At approximately 1:00, when the crime occurred,\Nwhere were you and what were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.68,0:22:18.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Around that time, I was in the dressing room...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.35,0:22:19.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Origami!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.89,0:22:21.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.31,0:22:25.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That devil said he was folding origami!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.98,0:22:27.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Origami?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.44,0:22:28.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Five cranes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.94,0:22:30.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looked like he was just killing time, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.61,0:22:34.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we can't tell anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.65,0:22:36.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otherwise he'll put a death curse on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.82,0:22:39.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A death curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.33,0:22:46.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what I tell the fans—it isn't a hobby befitting of a devil, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.00,0:22:48.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.46,0:22:52.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you were in the dressing room by yourself\Nthe whole time up until the children came?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.42,0:22:58.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I ate the delivered food, took a nap, and folded origami.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.30,0:23:02.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you were here at the TV station quite some time\Nbefore you were scheduled to make your appearance?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.97,0:23:06.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went to the dressing room a bit before 11:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.56,0:23:11.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Immediately afterward, I had my manager take\Nmy food order and go buy some things for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.52,0:23:12.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.32,0:23:17.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I came back, the children were about to enter\NSatan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s dressing room, so I stopped them at first...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.24,0:23:21.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since I was told not to wake him until\Nhe was to go to the studio at 2:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.74,0:23:22.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.91,0:23:28.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, in short, when the murder occurred at\Napproximately 1:00 PM, you have no alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.71,0:23:31.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but it would've been impossible for me anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.88,0:23:35.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I'd come out of my dressing room with this face and\Nloitered around, it'd definitely have attracted attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.13,0:23:39.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get all the station personnel together and ask them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.30,0:23:42.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Find out if there's anyone who had seen\Nme during the time in question.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.06,0:23:45.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, if you removed the makeup and left with your true face...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.93,0:23:46.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.98,0:23:50.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you went through the station using your true\Nface and headed towards the meeting room...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.23,0:23:52.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, after committing the crime, reapplied the makeup...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.15,0:23:54.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe that'd be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.03,0:23:56.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.69,0:23:59.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does it take that long to apply the makeup?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.53,0:24:02.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it would only take about 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.45,0:24:06.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Except for the fact that there are no mirrors in that dressing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.41,0:24:09.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are no...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.29,0:24:09.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mirrors?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.50,0:24:17.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was an influential actor who hated mirrors more than anything,\Nso there are two or three dressing rooms like that here, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.26,0:24:21.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} always uses one of those dressing rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.09,0:24:22.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hate mirrors too, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.35,0:24:25.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Especially big ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.81,0:24:28.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you'd like, you can take a look at the dressing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.53,0:24:39.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It certainly seems that there are no mirrors on the walls...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.16,0:24:42.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.32,0:24:45.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is one, isn't there!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.53,0:24:46.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.87,0:24:49.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just bought that mirror and brought it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.25,0:24:54.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I gave it to Satan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} when I came in with the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.46,0:24:58.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, please share which store it's from so I may confirm it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.51,0:24:59.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.34,0:25:05.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, if you would, please let us investigate this dressing\Nroom and Satan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s belongings, as well as his person.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.10,0:25:06.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.39,0:25:08.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.43,0:25:12.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inside the bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.81,0:25:15.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like there are various supplies for applying makeup, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.65,0:25:17.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There aren't any mirrors...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.73,0:25:19.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,None on his person, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.07,0:25:24.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with this slightly dirty jacket and hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.20,0:25:26.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the chest, it says "Devil Shop"...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.16,0:25:32.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I brought that to use in the scene in today's\Ntalk show where I first come on stage...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.12,0:25:36.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During our live performances, we always\Ndo a short skit in between songs...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.42,0:25:38.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good day, l am the devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.25,0:25:40.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have come to deliver misfortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.51,0:25:42.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We do that sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.92,0:25:46.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, confirm with the program's staff just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.05,0:25:47.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.05,0:25:51.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, the makeup supplies are used\Nfor touch-ups during the performance...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.81,0:25:56.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's just a slight touch-up, I can borrow a compact\Nmirror from one of the female staff members and fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.90,0:26:00.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't sweat much, so it rarely happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.78,0:26:04.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it looks like that purple lipstick\Ncomes off pretty easily, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.78,0:26:06.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, from Satan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s cigarette butts.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.99,0:26:09.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's purple coloring on the filters...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.74,0:26:13.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the same color is all over the autograph\Nboard that Mitsuhiko received from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.04,0:26:14.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.75,0:26:15.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.21,0:26:20.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the time, Satan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} used his mouth to remove the cap.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.38,0:26:22.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how the purple color got on the cap...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.09,0:26:26.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the color got onto your hand from\Nthe pen that he handed back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.22,0:26:31.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because you were holding it with that hand this whole time,\Nyou transferred the color onto the board without realizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.60,0:26:32.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.72,0:26:33.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.60,0:26:34.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah-le-le...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.60,0:26:35.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's strange, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.23,0:26:41.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no purple color on the chopsticks or spoon\Nfrom the delivered food that Satan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} ate...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.27,0:26:43.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though they'd all come into contact with his mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.65,0:26:44.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.32,0:26:47.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That certainly is odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.07,0:26:52.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I eat, I take the lipstick off with a tissue.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.12,0:26:54.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't like getting purple all over the chopsticks and the bowl...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.08,0:26:58.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's just the lipstick, I can easily reapply it without a mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.08,0:27:01.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then do you use the lipstick around your eyes too?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.80,0:27:03.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the same purple color...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.01,0:27:07.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not lipstick, but it's from the same brand.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.01,0:27:09.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, that cannot be done without a mirror...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.43,0:27:16.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if there are people who can put it on themselves\Nwithout a mirror, they might be gods or devils themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.77,0:27:18.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That much is true...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.60,0:27:21.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Devil{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} sure likes that purple color!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.86,0:27:25.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's a color that I've liked since we were still indie.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.07,0:27:27.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No other brand makes this color.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.03,0:27:30.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, since today isn't a live performance...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.74,0:27:35.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The white for the face and the gray for the cheeks can be\Ndone with a readily available water-soluble foundat—
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.16,0:27:39.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.71,0:27:42.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} has dry eyes because he's wearing contacts...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.38,0:27:45.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, your eye drops.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.59,0:27:46.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.18,0:27:50.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But your eyes—they're red.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.80,0:27:52.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I said it's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.39,0:27:53.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just drop it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.39,0:27:56.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.31,0:28:02.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't find any mirrors in this dressing room, or my bags, or\Non my person, so tell me how I could've done my makeup!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.69,0:28:04.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The food delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.53,0:28:09.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For example, after committing the crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.74,0:28:18.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could have secretly given the mirror that you used to fix your\Nmakeup to one of the three people who delivered the food here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.88,0:28:28.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Certainly, if he did that...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.97,0:28:30.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.97,0:28:33.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just asked the guards at the doors...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.68,0:28:39.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The food couriers that came before the body was discovered at\N2:00 were only those three, and they all came at around noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.10,0:28:42.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I asked all three of them just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.15,0:28:44.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They confirmed that they brought the food at roughly 12:00...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.36,0:28:49.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that they were told by Satan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to\Ncome back for the plates in the evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.69,0:28:51.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They haven't come back to collect the plates yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.65,0:28:57.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, of course, all three said that when they delivered\Nhe food, Satan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had his makeup on as usual
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.20,0:29:04.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they delivered the food before the crime was committed, he\Ncouldn't have passed the mirror to one of them after the fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.79,0:29:07.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The remaining possibility is that, when the\Nassistant director came to call them...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.63,0:29:12.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He threw away the mirror he had hidden\Nwhile hurrying to the scene of the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.89,0:29:15.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think that's the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.60,0:29:18.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was watching him the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.51,0:29:20.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was only running normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.85,0:29:21.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.23,0:29:28.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, the manager bought that mirror at around 12:30 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.48,0:29:32.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From that shop to this television station,\Nit takes about an hour by car...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.45,0:29:34.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it's impossible for him to have brought it before the crime, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.82,0:29:40.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, there's no mistake that the food delivery\Ncostume was scheduled to be used in the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.20,0:29:43.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The station even had the delivery box prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.54,0:29:47.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But do you really play the food delivery person with that makeup on?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.59,0:29:49.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we do it at our live shows a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.38,0:29:53.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My hair is set well enough that wearing a hat won't affect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.80,0:29:56.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, where did you\Nmake yourself up into this devil form?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.80,0:29:59.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were already like this when you entered the dressing room...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.64,0:30:01.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At home!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.10,0:30:06.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd already finished doing it at home, come to the station\Nby car, parked the car in the parking lot, and arrived here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.86,0:30:09.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, I had my manager take the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.61,0:30:12.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I had a bag on me while made up\Nlike this, it'd be strange, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.90,0:30:16.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, were you smoking when you folded the origami?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.24,0:30:18.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I usually smoke while performing detailed tasks.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.45,0:30:20.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.83,0:30:25.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope, no problem—I was just curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.33,0:30:27.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.29,0:30:29.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.18,0:30:38.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Sun has gone down...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.97,0:30:40.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.31,0:30:42.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought, the culprit is this person.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.64,0:30:45.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely, he temporarily removed his makeup\Nand did the deed wearing his true face.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.56,0:30:49.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And after killing the president, he reapplied\Nthe makeup and became a devil again.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.57,0:30:51.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's a problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.69,0:30:55.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When did he acquire the mirror needed for\Nthe makeup, and where did he hide it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.57,0:30:59.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are a number of bathrooms on the\Nroute from here to the meeting room...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.03,0:31:02.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if he had used one of those, he'd have been seen for certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.50,0:31:05.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if he was lucky and wasn't seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.96,0:31:09.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt that someone would have\Nremembered him in the hallway with that getup on.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.00,0:31:13.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he hid his face, it would attract even more attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.71,0:31:17.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess it makes more sense that he came back to\Nthe dressing room and reapplied the makeup.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.93,0:31:21.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those origami cranes bother me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.56,0:31:27.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he was planning on using the idea that he wasn't able to commit\Nthe murder due to his folding cranes as an alibi, five are too few...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.77,0:31:32.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, he should have been able to foresee that someone could just point\Nout that the cranes could have been brought here inside the bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.07,0:31:33.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that his alibi would fold just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.61,0:31:38.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, what do the cranes and origami mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.24,0:31:42.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Couldn't this be the mirror?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.49,0:31:44.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, in this window...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.08,0:31:46.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and Mitsuhiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} are clearly reflected!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.62,0:31:51.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, but take a good look.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.67,0:31:53.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Little girl, can you see your own face?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.30,0:31:56.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, it's dark and you can't really see it, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.72,0:31:58.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.47,0:32:00.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you get too close to it, it becomes dark and you can't see clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.34,0:32:05.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The crime occurred in the middle of the day, at around 1:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.72,0:32:06.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was bright out.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.81,0:32:08.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it doesn't get dark, it can't reflect.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.64,0:32:11.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, that's the reason for the origami!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.73,0:32:17.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm finally able to see it—the trick you used to hide your devilish form!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.28,0:32:20.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Professor, where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.16,0:32:22.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry there...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.87,0:32:24.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My cell phone ran out of power...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.74,0:32:27.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went to contact everyone's parents using the public telephone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.58,0:32:28.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, detectives!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.91,0:32:30.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you found your answer yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.67,0:32:36.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I had come out of this dressing room with this face and roamed around\Nthe station, nine times out of ten someone would've spotted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.71,0:32:40.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've said this earlier, but if I murdered the company president...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.43,0:32:44.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To get to the meeting room two floors above this one,\NI'd have to temporarily remove my makeup...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.51,0:32:47.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And reapply it here after committing the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.43,0:32:49.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.64,0:32:51.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The mirror that would have been essential to this task doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.27,0:32:55.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, it doesn't exist in my bag or on my person, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.23,0:32:59.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only mirror here is the one that my\Nmanager bought and brought here for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.94,0:33:03.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it only came into my hands after the time of the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.36,0:33:06.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And at that time, I was already dressed like this with my makeup on.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.95,0:33:07.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.83,0:33:08.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.62,0:33:11.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't just me—those children were also present.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.12,0:33:14.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without a mirror, I can't paint this face.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.67,0:33:16.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.50,0:33:22.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why, after I entered this television station today,\NI had this costume on the entire time up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.18,0:33:27.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So please, will you leave me alone and let me\Nmourn the death of my company president?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.68,0:33:30.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't cry in front of others while still calling myself a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.10,0:33:32.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.35,0:33:33.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.90,0:33:35.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At least let me take off this makeup, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.31,0:33:37.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be done in three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.48,0:33:42.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it weren't for this face, no one would notice me even if I cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.15,0:33:44.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.32,0:33:46.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you want to wipe it away along with your makeup, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.20,0:33:52.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The evidence that proves that you really are a devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.54,0:33:57.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those flame-colored remnants.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.01,0:34:04.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.43,0:34:07.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Using my voice without permission again...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.76,0:34:09.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of joke is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.56,0:34:10.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.81,0:34:14.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It certainly is impossible for you to have\Nwandered around in that getup...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.31,0:34:19.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if you removed your makeup and wore the food\Ndelivery costume, no one would have noticed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.82,0:34:23.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you had delivery personnel from three different shops come.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.07,0:34:29.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In short, at around the time of the murder, those three\Nfood delivery people came in and out of this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.45,0:34:32.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were able to slip in amongst them to comm it the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.87,0:34:36.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If their uniforms were similar, it'd be even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.08,0:34:39.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those that would have seen you would\Nnot have paid attention to your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.09,0:34:44.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, could it be that the clothes he\Nwore then were the ones in the bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.67,0:34:49.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Correct, he used the "Devil Shop" costume\Nthat was intended for the talk show.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.47,0:34:52.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're speaking as if you'd actually seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.77,0:34:55.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly—I did see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.27,0:34:59.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time, a strange food delivery\Nperson running without a delivery box...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.48,0:35:02.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.69,0:35:05.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A food delivery person would normally have\Na delivery box in their hand, wouldn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.03,0:35:07.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Both coming and going...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.91,0:35:10.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this is a television station.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.20,0:35:13.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Occasionally there would be an actor wearing such a costume...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.62,0:35:19.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did think that for a moment, but no matter the role,\Nthey'd at least put on some simple makeup.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.21,0:35:23.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even so, that man was wearing only his true face.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.46,0:35:29.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what's more, the bottom part of his head that I was able to see\Nunder the cap was exactly the same inverted-V style as Satan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.14,0:35:34.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's no evidence that that delivery person was me, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.48,0:35:38.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are other people who have the same haircut as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.02,0:35:41.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They could even have been one of my fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.61,0:35:49.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Plus, if I murdered the president like that, how did\NI reapply this makeup after I came back here?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.99,0:35:52.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Certainly, there's no mirror in this room...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.33,0:35:55.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you can make one, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.08,0:35:56.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Using a transparent board.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.58,0:35:58.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Transparent...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.54,0:35:59.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Board?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.96,0:36:04.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're talking about this window glass, it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.88,0:36:10.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like the children said, if you get too close to it as if you were putting\Non makeup, your face becomes a shadow and can't be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.76,0:36:13.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And since the crime was committed during the day,\Nnothing would have been reflected anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.06,0:36:15.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know what it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.64,0:36:17.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit didn't use the glass...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.60,0:36:19.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was that ruler!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.40,0:36:22.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ruler?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.19,0:36:24.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.65,0:36:27.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the same as the window glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.53,0:36:30.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you use this origami and make it dark, it'll work.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.20,0:36:33.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will that really turn it into a mirror?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.62,0:36:34.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do it, do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.95,0:36:42.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, window glass and this sort of\Ntransparent plastic reflect light all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.21,0:36:43.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't see anything being reflected!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.84,0:36:47.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's only because the light from this side\Nis so strong that you can't see it clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.51,0:36:51.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if you do this, and put the black origami\Nbehind it to obstruct the light...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.84,0:36:54.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It really is being reflected!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.22,0:36:58.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true, amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.39,0:36:59.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's like a mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.31,0:37:06.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, as far as the nighttime window glass, what's\Nreflected gets dark and hard to see due to the shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.90,0:37:09.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what's reflected is a far cry from the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.90,0:37:12.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't clearly see the color.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.20,0:37:16.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, what if we use silver?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.99,0:37:19.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, we can see the color this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.91,0:37:22.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's blurry and you can't see very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.37,0:37:29.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Silver has the power to reflect, but because the\Nsurface of the paper is rough, it becomes blurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.80,0:37:32.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's all right even if you can't see the color.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.43,0:37:36.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s makeup is such that it's always a matter\Nof painting a certain color on a certain area.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.76,0:37:37.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.89,0:37:40.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's like that, then it seems that you\Nreally could apply your makeup here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.14,0:37:41.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.02,0:37:42.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In short, Satan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.23,0:37:48.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Removed his makeup immediately after the deliverers\Nbrought the food and, wearing the delivery uniform...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.27,0:37:51.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Headed to the meeting room where the president was.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.40,0:37:56.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the murder, he quickly returned here, reapplied\Nthe makeup using the mirror made from the ruler...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.95,0:37:59.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And waited for the manager to come wake him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.54,0:38:07.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if that's the case, there should have been a lot of blood\Nspatter on this delivery uniform from the company president...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.50,0:38:10.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he probably prepared a different sort of clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.09,0:38:13.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For example, something like a raincoat that had a hood attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.22,0:38:16.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, mobilize the investigators arid find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.68,0:38:17.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.64,0:38:22.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if that sort of thing is found, it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.85,0:38:25.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't do it, and you have no proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.73,0:38:28.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Making a mirror out of the ruler and origami?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.52,0:38:29.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How would I know about something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.57,0:38:35.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was only in here folding origami cranes\Nwhile waiting for my manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.07,0:38:39.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, if that's the case, I wonder if you could fold one for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.24,0:38:40.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Another origami crane.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.04,0:38:41.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.95,0:38:44.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't mind if you smoke...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.58,0:38:47.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you do detailed tasks, you like to smoke, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.04,0:38:49.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.67,0:38:51.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could I fold one in these circumstances?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.88,0:38:54.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, could you fold one in his place?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.05,0:38:57.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, you make a triangle...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.01,0:38:59.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.93,0:39:01.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.10,0:39:02.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're really good, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.68,0:39:06.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When my dad was in the hospital, Mom\Nand I folded a whole bunch, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.31,0:39:08.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, done!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.73,0:39:13.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a well-made crane, but it's skinny\Nand doesn't look very healthy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.82,0:39:14.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.28,0:39:18.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.62,0:39:23.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must blow into origami cranes in order to make them expand.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.41,0:39:26.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you did apply your mouth there, your\Nlipstick would have rubbed off on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.21,0:39:28.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like the cigarette butts in the ashtray.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.29,0:39:30.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there is none on your cranes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.09,0:39:34.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So then, does that mean he didn't fold those\Ncranes today with his makeup on?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.76,0:39:38.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Agasa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, do you even know what you're talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.98,0:39:40.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.18,0:39:45.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whatever the case may be, whether Satan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Ncan't fold the cranes or forgot how...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.77,0:39:52.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The point is that those cranes were folded beforehand, and\Nbrought here in order to camouflage the mirror trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.48,0:39:58.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason why he deliberately offered up to you detective\Nthe fact that he held a grudge against the president...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.03,0:40:03.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was so that you could immediately come to his dressing\Nroom and confirm that there was, in fact, no mirror there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.78,0:40:09.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it were later, the food delivery personnel would\Nhave returned to collect the plates and bowls...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.62,0:40:12.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the possibility of the presence of\Na mirror would have become unclear.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.13,0:40:18.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the reason he asked the food delivery personnel to return in\Nthe evening was so that he could allow time for us to investigate?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.76,0:40:20.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.68,0:40:23.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} would never murder anyone—it just can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.64,0:40:29.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, I wonder if you could take that makeup\Noff here, and show us your true face.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.39,0:40:31.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.10,0:40:32.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, let's remove your makeup.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.40,0:40:36.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.36,0:40:41.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I can't, Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.91,0:40:45.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I peel off this devil's mask...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.58,0:40:49.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The shameful face of a murderer will be revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.62,0:40:51.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No... It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.92,0:40:55.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know about what happened three years ago, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.04,0:40:58.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The story of when, in the middle of a tour, I\Nhad to be hospitalized due to throat pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.76,0:41:02.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Back then, there was a child that sent me\Na letter wishing me well every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.47,0:41:06.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Along with a small box containing a folded origami crane.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.35,0:41:10.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She believed that I was actually a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.98,0:41:13.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was so happy to read those letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.27,0:41:17.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But one day, the letters from that child stopped coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.24,0:41:22.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the time, I thought that maybe she'd just lost interest...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.07,0:41:26.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But last month...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.62,0:41:29.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I went drinking with the president,\Nthe reason behind it was revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.20,0:41:34.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That man said: "Should we make another\Nsacrifice in order to push you to glory?"
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.42,0:41:35.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A sacrifice?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.63,0:41:36.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.17,0:41:39.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I was hospitalized, I didn't know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.26,0:41:44.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the band's homepage, the company president\Nmade comments in my name without my permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.51,0:41:48.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"In order for my powers to return, I need a sacrifice... I want blood!"
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.35,0:41:51.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that that fan took it seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.27,0:41:56.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.19,0:41:59.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I pressed the issue with him, he laughed...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.32,0:42:05.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saying that the last letter read, "I am overjoyed\Nto present you with my blood. Goodbye."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.45,0:42:12.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The live comeback performance a half-month later was much more\Npopular than before I was hospitalized and before someone died.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.71,0:42:16.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I immediately searched for and went to visit that\Nchild's home and found out that, sure enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.96,0:42:19.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She apparently committed suicide for unknown reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.71,0:42:22.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, it was revenge for that child?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.26,0:42:24.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I did him in!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.30,0:42:26.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That man who, for the sake of money,\Ndidn't give a damn about human life...,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.51,0:42:30.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who destroyed the live breakup performance that I'd\Nworked so hard to set up without having been asked...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.97,0:42:34.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And insisting that I'd have to pay damages if I\Nwanted to break the contract and retire early...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.73,0:42:38.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That real devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.03,0:42:43.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I gave you a nice list of reasons, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.19,0:42:46.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've actually been in a slump these past two\Nyears and just wanted to end things early...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.61,0:42:49.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That may have been the real reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.62,0:42:53.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But my sister said...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.04,0:42:56.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The Styx Three will definitely make a comeback!"
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.62,0:43:00.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that they'd definitely come up with some\Nmarvelous songs, boiling over with spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.63,0:43:02.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.59,0:43:07.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I say things like "I'll possess you," and "I'll put a\Ndeath curse on you," but I've never said "Die."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.51,0:43:10.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only ones who babble things like\Nthat are villains from Kamen Yaiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.60,0:43:17.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've become that sort of man, I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.56,0:43:18.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.73,0:43:19.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know what else?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.86,0:43:22.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the letters from that child stopped, it really bothered me...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.44,0:43:24.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I kept thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.40,0:43:27.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Did I do something wrong to make her hate me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.95,0:43:30.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I started thinking like that, I began to cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.99,0:43:33.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I couldn't write songs or lyrics...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.33,0:43:34.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not even one phrase...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.41,0:43:36.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not qualified to be a devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.62,0:43:39.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.42,0:43:41.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Devil{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s tears are a little red...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.67,0:43:44.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because of President Urushibara's blood spatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.59,0:43:45.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.47,0:43:54.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember how you couldn't see color very\Nwell in the mirror made from the ruler?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.72,0:43:59.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without noticing the blood under his eyes,\Nhe put the white foundation over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.10,0:44:04.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He finally realized it when he gazed in\Nthe mirror the manager brought him.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.86,0:44:07.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he didn't use the eye drops...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.49,0:44:11.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because if the eye drops were to overflow, the\Nconclusive evidence would have made itself known.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.20,0:44:12.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.41,0:44:14.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.33,0:44:19.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's just like a fairy tale, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.04,0:44:27.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's often said that if the devil cries, he loses his powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.72,0:46:01.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, the game has turned serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.52,0:46:06.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inoue Waka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, Okino Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} san{\r}, and\NYamamoto Azusa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} san{\r} are tied for the lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.98,0:46:08.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's only one question left!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.07,0:46:12.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The winner will be determined by this last question!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.49,0:46:17.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, this program was recorded when\Nyou all were at the station, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.07,0:46:21.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but we didn't meet with Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} after the case\Nwas over, so we didn't find out what the results were.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.29,0:46:27.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, there's no doubt the winner will\Nbe the beautiful and amazing Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.79,0:46:29.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inoue{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, how's your confidence level?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.25,0:46:31.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.97,0:46:33.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okino{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.26,0:46:36.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please support me, fans!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.97,0:46:39.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All the way, Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}! I support you!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.44,0:46:40.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yamamoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.39,0:46:42.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Azu will also do her best!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.06,0:46:44.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right then, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.06,0:46:46.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The 10th question!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.61,0:46:52.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you say Conan Doyle, it would be Sherlock Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.23,0:46:55.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you say Yokomizo Seishi, it'd be Kindaichi Kousuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.15,0:46:57.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So then, if you say Edogawa Ranpo?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.95,0:47:00.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.70,0:47:01.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, Okino{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.67,0:47:08.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akechi! Akechi!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.92,0:47:11.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's too bad! Okino{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} has been disqualified!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.09,0:47:14.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The winners are Inoue Waka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Yamamoto Azusa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.01,0:47:15.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's have a round of applause!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.51,0:47:16.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Congrats!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.88,0:47:18.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.30,0:47:21.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, saying that name even by accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.35,0:47:24.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri! Kogorou!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.93,0:47:27.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You make me lose hope.
